s observing stars, planets, comets, and galaxies using telescopes and space-based instruments."], "scores": [0.812366070323889, 0.6774955036146539, 0.5437795009980533, 0.5205215093087358, 0.5134715110516168], "model_name": "bge-large", "document_ids": ["Robotics", "Cybernetics", "Neuroscience", "Ecology", "Astronomy"]}}